Scala starter package for Google Planet Wars AI contest

http://ai-contest.com/

Install Scala 2.8 (http://www.scala-lang.org/)

To build:
scalac *scala

To test it:
java -jar tools/PlayGame.jar maps/map1.txt 3000 3000 log.txt "scala MyBot" "scala MyBot" | java -jar tools/ShowGame.jar

Keep in mind that the JVM may took more than 1 second to initialize on the first turn, hence test it with 2 or 3 seconds (the 3000 parameter above)
